p: GC-MS analysis was examined by an Agilent 6890N GC and Agilent 5975 GC/MSD systems (Agilent Technologies, SEM Ltd., Istanbul, Turkey). HP-Innowax FSC column (60 m × 0.25 mm, 0.25 μm film thickness (Agilent Technologies) was used with a helium carrier gas at 0.8 mL/min as reported previously [24].
